Morgan Stanley says the capital provided by MUFG will enable it to seize investment opportunities, strengthen its balance sheet and increase its liquidity.
A spokeswoman for the group declined to elaborate on the strategic plans of the two new allies.
After MUFG's investment, Morgan Stanley should show a Tier One Solvency Ratio of close to 15%, one of the best in the industry.
Morgan needed to ease his balance sheet a lot since late August.
